Libre Caslon Text Italic (LibreCaslonText-Italic.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'LibreCaslonText-Italic', Everything looks good.

Pass

MS NID 6

NID 6 is 'LibreCaslonText-Medium', Everything looks good.

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Libre Caslon Text' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Medium' = NID 1 'Libre Caslon Text Medium'.

Libre Caslon Text Bold Italic (LibreCaslonText-BoldItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'LibreCaslonText-BoldItalic', Everything looks good.

Libre Caslon Text Bold Italic (LibreCaslonText-BoldItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Libre Caslon Text' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Bold Italic' = NID 1 'Libre Caslon Text Bold' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.
